sequenceDiagram
    participant Handler
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Worker as Outbox Worker
    participant Broker as Message Broker (RabbitMQ/Kafka)
    
    Handler->>DB: 1. Begin Transaction
    Handler->>DB: 2. Insert Business Data (e.g. Booking)
    Handler->>DB: 3. Insert OutboxMessage (Event)
    Handler->>DB: 4. Commit Transaction
    
    loop Background Process
        Worker->>DB: 5. Read Pending Messages
        Worker->>Broker: 6. Publish Event
        Worker->>DB: 7. Mark as Processed
    end
